%%BeginDocument: midptf.eps
%!PS-Adobe-3.0 EPSF-3.0
%%Creator: MATLAB, The Mathworks, Inc.
%%Title: /home/math/rossi/courses/2002_spring/Math428/lectures/midptf.eps
